ACGlass Notices
================

ACGlass is a derived Android-container GUI project. It includes new ACGlass
launcher, Droidspaces integration, container app scanning, and single-app
window startup work.

Upstream code and project references:

- anland - android wayland implement
  https://github.com/superturtlee/anland

  Portions of this repository are derived from the anland project, including
  the Android Wayland display path, display daemon/consumer/producer structure,
  and Weston Anland backend work. The upstream repository did not expose an
  explicit license file in the GitHub repository view at the time this notice
  was added. Keep this attribution when reusing ACGlass code derived from
  anland.

- Droidspaces OSS - android container implement
  https://github.com/ravindu644/Droidspaces-OSS

  ACGlass integrates with the Droidspaces CLI and targets Droidspaces
  containers as its first supported Android container backend. Droidspaces OSS
  is a separate project and is not bundled as source code in this repository.
